article.headline: Peek-Green scores 21 as Alabama A&M downs UAPB 63-62
article.description: — -- — Omari Peek-Green scored 21 points and Lorenzo Downey had a block in the final seconds as Alabama A&M beat UAPB 63-62 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Peek-Green scores 21 as Alabama A&M downs UAPB 63-62
article.story: PINE BLUFF, Ark. -- — -- — Omari Peek-Green scored 21 points and Lorenzo Downey had a block in the final seconds as Alabama A&M beat UAPB 63-62 on Saturday night. Peek-Green had six rebounds for the Bulldogs (2-12, 1-0 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Downey scored eight points while going 4 of 9 (0 for 3 from 3-point range), and added 13 rebounds. Cameron Tucker had six points and finished 3 of 6 from the field. The victory snapped a seven-game slide for the Bulldogs. Lonnell Martin Jr. finished with 20 points for the Golden Lions (5-9, 0-1). UAPB also got 15 points, seven rebounds and four steals from Ismael Plet. In addition, Kylen Milton had 12 points, four assists and four steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
